description: Louisville's very own Louisville Sushi truck claiming ground in the derby city. The perfect way to catch someone eye and taste with a bright red sushi truck rolling up some of the fresh and best tasting sushi rolls Kentucky can offer. The great sushi meals are meant to be enjoyed on the go. Louisville Sushi popular menu has led them to be the to go place for sushi. No need to wait and spend top dollar for restaurant quality sushi, just follow the Louisville Sushi Truck where it's Fast-Fresh-Street Style!
name: Louisville Sushi Truck
